  "projectType": "sdk-library",
  "projectName": "Polly",
  "projectDescription": "A .NET resilience and transient-fault-handling library that allows developers to express policies such as Retry, Circuit Breaker, Timeout, Bulkhead Isolation, Rate Limiter, Hedging, and Fallback in a fluent and thread-safe manner.",
